{"tid":10522,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"飛機Post 就快去睇X Japan電影 一齊講下初次接觸X Japan","createTime":"2016-11-29T03:41:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-11T02:39:49.000Z","uid":5716,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4d9969ff3d5fc0a091f313cbbc9ecfa5e2e34831","tid":10522,"uid":5716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T03:41:37.000Z","msg":"係好細個果陣，跟表姐同佢男朋友去食X祿壽司，食食下聽到電視有條友We Are We Are咁鳩叫，心諗做咩撚野。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WiDHA63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWiDHA63.jpg&h=e6e1f04e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇左陣就問表姐唱歌條友係咪盲？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/29/113146_3ff59a23634fa2301a782606ba4bd886.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F113146_3ff59a23634fa2301a782606ba4bd886.jpg&h=5fda256b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n粉紅色頭髮果個女人黎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/29/113230_19f37598b5e446e8eddcf26490dd4e5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F113230_19f37598b5e446e8eddcf26490dd4e5b.jpg&h=452e811a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鼓手仲咩帶住頸cool仲要打鼓打得咁激動又成日好似想喊咁?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o8bd0uN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo8bd0uN.jpg&h=18397215&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正常人一號，仲咩成日陰陰咀咁笑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/29/113423_f8c5259430a6a0cba7e52d3743ab56f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F113423_f8c5259430a6a0cba7e52d3743ab56f4.jpg&h=2067dc6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當時覺得呢個係正常人二號，但無咩特別。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後表姐見我對X Japan有好奇心，就俾左幾隻CD同DVD我，記得有X Japan，Luna Sea 同Glay。唔聽由自可，一聽就返唔到轉頭，除左Glay之外，X Japan同Luna Sea就變左我杯茶。過左無耐，就見到hide坐住火箭既相佔據左娛樂頭版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。果下直頭覺得自己生遲左幾年，早d出世就可以了解佢地多d。<br />\n<br />\n以上係小弟第一次接觸X Japan既情況，有機會既話可以一齊討論下佢地既歌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> We are X"},{"pid":"ede7aa12fd347fb92f43dbcd23b2e0207b75be9d","tid":10522,"uid":18685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T03:44:59.000Z","msg":"買左飛12月睇we are X<br />\n<br />\nE一刻, 我係聽緊art of life~"},{"pid":"abdb4b5aa14da843cb2f070283aa3a1124d1ac17","tid":10522,"uid":5716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T04:05:44.000Z","msg":"講多少少，另一個X Japan既成員Taiji，92年被Y<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/29/114727_da19f393f4edad8d6ffb3b4c113898d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F114727_da19f393f4edad8d6ffb3b4c113898d1.jpg&h=d9f82be3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小弟私心覺得Taiji編既Bass豐富好多，Bass 既旋律好靚。可惜92年係YOSHIKI的要求下離開樂團，開始地獄一樣既下半生。"},{"pid":"dccd08431dfc23fd7d09a3c85108248ae31dc07f","tid":10522,"uid":5716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T04:08:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買左飛12月睇we are X<br />\n<br />\nE一刻, 我係聽緊art of life~</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 29分鐘，有時返工放工都會聽，聽完岩岩好一程車。"},{"pid":"20fc92cbbfd7a939a0c1f9caec23e0c4db224d74","tid":10522,"uid":38420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T04:36:49.000Z","msg":"中學開始聽x Japan 覺得d歌正 之後覺得鼓手yoshiki好撚型 跟住就走左去學鼓 🤘🤘🤘呢隊band真心好傳奇 除左d歌序外 個background都好正 雖然而家個個都係阿叔 但真心覺得真係好有味道 聽左就返唔到轉頭 踏上左聽jrock既不歸路😢😢"},{"pid":"76ad23ffd60c23c19df8f05dc26d02ea64436b56","tid":10522,"uid":38420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T04:37:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中學開始聽x Japan 覺得d歌正 之後覺得鼓手yoshiki好撚型 跟住就走左去學鼓 🤘🤘🤘呢隊band真心好傳奇 除左d歌之外 個background都好正 雖然而家個個都係阿叔 但真心覺得好有味道 聽左就返唔到轉頭 踏上左聽jrock既不歸路😢😢</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c33ac12ee30f9243a6925910c08615b73023c6fc","tid":105